Wasu 'yan majalisa sun sha wahala saboda shawarar da aka yi na sauya sunayensu zuwa MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament).
Wannan ya taso ne saboda akwai shirin sauya sunan majalisa zuwa Welsh Parliament.
Masu sha'awar siyasa suna damuwa da cewa zai iya yin kudi daga gare su.
Wani dan majalisa daga jam'iyyar Labour ya nuna cewa jam'iyyarsa na tsoron cewa ya yi daidai da Twp da Pwp.
Ga masu karatu a wajen Wales: A cikin Welsh twp na nufin raba kuma pwp na nufin shitty.
Wani dan majalisa daga Plaid ya ce kungiyar ta kasance mai cin hanci da rashawa, kuma ta binciki wasu hanyoyin.
Wani daga cikin jam'iyyar mai ra'ayin mazan jiya ya ce kungiyarsa ta kasance "marasa damuwa" game da canjin sunan, amma ya yi gargadin cewa wani ɗan gajeren lokaci ne daga MWP zuwa Muppet.
A wannan mahallin, ana gabatar da harafin Welsh w kamar yadda aka gabatar da harafin u a cikin Yorkshire Turanci.
Kwamitin majalisar da ke zaman majalisar dokokin da ke gabatar da wannan sauyi ya ce: "Tabbas, membobin majalisar ne za su yanke hukunci na karshe kan yadda za a yi wa majalisar magana".
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017, ta ba Majalisar Wales ikon canza sunanta.
A watan Yuni kwamitin ya sanar da sakamakon wani babban shawarwari kan batun, wanda ya ce mafiya rinjaye na goyon bayan kiran majalisa a Welsh Parliament.
A cikin batun kiran 'yan majalisa, kwamitin ya kasance ga' yan majalisa na Welsh ko WMP, amma zaɓin MWP ya sami mafi kyawun goyon baya a cikin shawarwari na gama gari.
'Yan majalisar sun bayyana cewa suna duba wasu hanyoyin, amma gwagwarmayar cimma yarjejeniya na iya zama babban abin da ya fi damuwa ga shugaban kasa, Elin Jones, wanda ake sa ran zai gabatar da wani kudurin doka game da canje-canjen a cikin' yan makonni.
Dokar sake fasalin za ta kuma ƙunshi wasu canje-canje ga yadda majalisa ke aiki, a yanzu dokoki game da rashin daidaito na majalisa da kuma shawarwarin kwamitin.
