Firayim Ministan Birtaniya, Theresa May ta halarci taron jam'iyyar Conservative Party a Birmingham, Birtaniya, ranar 29 ga watan Satumba, 2018.
A wata hira da ta yi, a shafinta na farko a jaridar, tsohon sakataren harkokin wajen ta, Boris Johnson, ya yi ta'aziya kan shirin da ake kira Chequers na Brexit, yana mai cewa, shawarar da aka bayar cewa Birtaniya da EU su tara haraji daga juna "ba shi da ma'ana".
Harbin Wayde Sims: 'Yan sanda sun kama Dyteon Simpson a karkashin zargin kisan dan wasan LSU.
'Yan sanda sun kama wanda ake zargi da harbin Wayde Sims, dan wasan kwallon kafa mai shekaru 20 a LSU.
An kama mutum mai suna Dyteon Simpson, mai shekara 20, kuma an tsare shi a kurkuku bisa zargin kisan kai, in ji sashen 'yan sanda na Baton Rouge.
Jami'an tsaro sun aika da hotunan rikicin tsakanin Sims da Simpson, kuma 'yan sanda sun ce Sims ya rasa tabarau a cikin rikici.
'Yan sanda sun gano tabarau a wurin kuma sun ce sun sami DNA na Simpson a kansu, in ji kamfanin CBS, WAFB.
Bayan da aka yi wa Simpson tambayoyi, 'yan sanda sun ce ya yarda da harbi da kashe Wayde.
An sanya belin a kan dala 350,000, in ji mai gabatar da kara.
Sashen binciken gawawwakin da ke yankin East Baton Rouge ya fitar da sanarwar farko a ranar Juma'a, inda ya ce dalilin mutuwar ta kasance harbi ne a kai da kuma wuyansa.
Sashen ya ba da kyauta ga rundunar 'yan sanda na Louisiana, da ofishin binciken aikata laifuka na' yan sanda, da' yan sanda na Jami'ar Kudancin da kuma wasu 'yan sanda a yankin, don taimakawa wajen binciken da ya kai ga kama shi.
Daraktan wasanni na LSU, Joe Alleva, ya gode wa 'yan sanda na yankin saboda "tausayi da kuma neman adalci".
Sims yana da shekara 20.
Mai tsayin 201 cm ya girma a Baton Rouge, inda mahaifinsa, Wayne, ya kuma buga wasan kwallon kafa na LSU.
Ya samu maki 5.6 da kuma rebounds 2.6 a matsakaici a kowane wasa a kakar wasa ta karshe.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a kocin kwallon kafa na LSU, Will Wade, ya ce kungiyar ta yi "kusa da komai" kuma ta yi "bacin rai" da mutuwar Wayde.
"Wannan shine abin da kuke damuwa akai-akai", in ji Wade.
