Scott Robinson ya yi birgima, amma ya tura kwallon a gaba kuma Alan Lithgow ya iya sarrafa kwallon a gaban raga, bayan ya zame don fuskantar mai tsinkaye Craig Halkett a gaba.
Masu masaukin sun yarda mu bar Rangers su yi kwallon, domin sun san cewa za su iya haifar da matsala ga baƙi a wuraren wasan kwallon kafa.
Kuma wannan shine yadda batun ya zo.
Rangers sun yi free kick kuma Livingston ya sami rami, kuma bayan rikici tsakanin Declan Gallagher da Robinson, an kawo wani shiri ga Menga, wanda ya yi motsi kuma ya zira kwallaye daga tsakiyar tseren.
