Sojoji sun yi harbi a wani gangamin lumana a filin a ranar 2 ga watan Oktoba, 1968, inda suka kashe mutane 300 a lokacin da zanga-zangar daliban hagu ta tashi a Latin Amurka.
Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin tallafa wa matasa 'yan Mexico ta hanyar ba da karatun wata-wata da kuma bude jami'o'i da yawa na jama'a.
Ya ce rashin aikin yi da rashin damar samun ilimi na janyo matasa zuwa garuruwan masu aikata laifuka.
Amurka ta ninka yawan masu amfani da AI.
Yayin da China ke kara shiga cikin bincike, Amurka za ta ninka yawan kudaden da take kashewa a bincike a wannan fannin, in ji babban mai saka jari Kai-Fu Lee, wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple.
Kalaman sun biyo bayan da dama a gwamnatin Amurka suka yi sanarwar rashin amincewa, ko da yake Amurka baki daya ba ta da wani shiri na amincewa.
A halin yanzu, kasar Sin ta gabatar da manufarta a bara: manufar ta ita ce ta kasance a kan gaba a cikin ingantaccen bidi'a kafin 2030.
"Abin farin ciki ne a ce, muna da kasafin kudi guda biyu domin mu samu karin kudi, saboda duk sauran kasashe suna baya da Amurka, kuma har yanzu muna neman matakin da ya dace don samun karin kudi", in ji Lee.
Rage farashin zai iya ninka yiwuwar cewa babban wasan kwaikwayon na gaba zai faru a Amurka, Lee ya ruwaito a cikin hira da CNBC a makon nan.
Lee, wanda littafinsa AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order aka buga a wannan watan ta Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, shi ne shugaban Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin da ke da karfin gaske a kasar Sin, Face++.
A cikin shekarun 1980 ya kasance a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon, inda ya yi aiki a kan tsarin da ya lashe gasar cin kofin duniya a wasan kwaikwayon Othello, kuma daga bisani ya zama shugaban Microsoft Research da shugaban Google a China.
Lee ya amince da gasar da gwamnatin Amurka ta yi a baya, yanzu gasar Robotics Challenge ta Hukumar Bincike ta Tsaro, kuma ya tambayi lokacin da na gaba zai ci gaba, don ya ga masu tunani na gaba.
Masu bincike a Amurka sau da yawa suna aiki tukuru don samun karbuwa a binciken jama'a, in ji Lee.
"Ba kasar Sin ce ke kawar da shugabannin ilimi ba, ayyukan ne", in ji Lee.
Facebook, Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun samu manyan mutane daga jami'o'i domin su yi aiki a kan wannan batu a cikin 'yan shekarun nan.
Lee ya ce sauye-sauyen manufofin shige da fice na iya zama da amfani ga Amurka, don tallafawa gwajin da hankali.
"Ina ganin ya kamata a ba da izinin aiki da kuma biyan bukatun kansu ga mutanen da ke da ilimin likita a hankali", in ji shi.
Majalisar Jiha ta kasar Sin ta sanar da shirin raya garuruwa na 'yan mata na gaba a watan Yuli na shekarar 2017.
National Natural Science Foundation na kasar Sin na ba da tallafi ga mutane a cibiyoyin ilimi, kamar yadda National Science Foundation da sauran hukumomin gwamnati ke ba da tallafi ga masu binciken Amurka, amma ingancin aikin kimiyya ya yi kasa a kasar Sin, in ji Lee.
A farkon wannan shekarar ne ma'aikatar tsaron Amurka ta kafa wani cibiyar hadin gwiwar kere kere da ke tattare da masu ruwa da tsaki daga masana'antu da kuma masana kimiyya, kuma fadar White House ta sanar da kafa kwamitin da aka zaba kan kere kere.
