Taron Trump a West Virginia, Tashar YouTube
Donald Trump, shugaban kasa, zai fara taron ne a wannan yamma a garin Wheeling, na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin tarurruka biyar da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tsayawa a wuraren maraba da ya yi a Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yanzu da barazanar zabensa na cike wa majalisar dattawa kujerar da ta yi wofi ke kara tashi, Trump na shirin karawa masu goyon baya a zaben da za a yi a tsakiyar watan nan, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar barazanar rasa ikon majalisa a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Taron Trump na yammacin Virginia yana gabatowa kuma yaya kake bincike a Intanet?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, an saita shi ne a karfe 19 na yammacin ranar Asabar, 29 ga watan Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a YouTube a ƙasa.
Da alama Trump zai tattauna batun shari'ar Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka nada a kotun koli a wannan makon, wani matsayi da ya fusata saboda zargin cin zarafin mata a cikin mukaminsa, inda aka dakatar da wani hukunci na majalisar dattijai har zuwa mako guda, yayin da FBI ke gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban manufar wannan taro shine taimaka wa 'yan Republican su yi zabe a watan Nuwamba.
Saboda haka, tawagar Trump ta sanar da cewa, wadannan tarurruka biyar na mako mai zuwa na nufin karfafa masu sa kai da kuma tallafawa, a yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma kara yawan kuri'unsu a majalisar dattawa da kuma wakilai, a cewar Reuters.
"Rashin cin zarafin da ake yi a majalisa na da muhimmanci sosai ga jadawalin taronsa, don haka shugaban zai ziyarci jihohi da dama kamar yadda zai yiwu, duk lokacin da muke gab da wani lokaci mai tsanani", in ji wani mai magana da yawun Trump, wanda ya ki ambaton sunansa, ya shaida wa Reuters.
Taron da za a yi a filin wasa na Wesbanco a Wheeling da yamma zai iya tattaro magoya bayan Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ya samu karbuwa a kafafen yada labarai a Pittsburgh, kamar yadda West Virginia Metro News ta ruwaito.
A ranar Asabar ne karo na biyu a cikin wata daya da Trump ya ziyarci jihar West Virginia, inda ya lashe zaben da kashi 40 cikin dari a 2016.
Trump na kokarin taimakawa dan takarar 'yan Republican na majalisar dattijai na West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke fafutukar neman zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrisey ba cewa shugaban kasa zai tilasta masa ya zo ya karfafa shi a zaben", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
