Muryar murna ta ƙara ƙaruwa, dukansu suna zagaye da shi, inda ya kama wani muhimmin bugun jini kuma ya daidaita a wasan na huɗu, bayan shi da Thomas sun kasance biyu a baya da biyu.
An yi wa ɗan wasan da ya ci nasara a kan rami na 15 murna da irin wannan ihu, irin wanda ya ba ka gargadi cewa ba ya tunanin cewa tawagar Amurka ta fita.
"Kawai ka tona zurfi ka yi tunanin ka", in ji Spieth.
Wannan shine abin da duk waɗannan 'yan wasan ke nema a yanzu.
18 ramuka don saita su sha'awa.
'Yan wasa guda daya da suka fi Spieth da Thomas maki a kwanaki biyu da suka gabata, sune Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, tarihin Ryder Cup.
Ma'aurata masu son yin nasara da kuma tunani a Turai suna da hudu daga cikin hudu kuma ba za su iya yin kuskure ba.
Mollwood shine kawai ma'aurata da ba su harba wani bogey a ranar Asabar ba, amma sun kuma gudanar da harbi a ranar Asabar da safe, ranar Juma'a da yamma a kan ramuka tara na karshe a ranar Juma'a.
Wannan tafiyar, duk da yadda guguwar ta yi kama da rafi zuwa da kuma daga mai kallo, ya tabbatar da cewa za su kasance masu nasara a ranar Lahadi, kuma 'yan wasan da suka fi shahara da za su iya tabbatar da nasarar Turai, yanzu rana ta sauka a Le Golf National, suna Fleetwood ko Molinari.
Zai fi kyau a yi duka a lokaci guda a cikin ramuka daban-daban.
Ba a magana sosai game da girmamawar Turai, duk da haka.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun yi saurin kawar da Sergio Garcia, gwarzon wasan Spain da kwallaye hudu a safiyar yau, lokacin da yake wasa da Alex Noren.
A bow and two doubles a farkon tara, suka haƙa Spaniard da filin wasa a cikin rami wanda ba su kusa fita ba.
Amma a ranar Lahadi, babu wanda zai taimake ka ka fita daga cikin rami.
Dukansu wasanni biyu da wasan wasan hudu suna da ban sha'awa don kallo daga nesa, saboda hulɗar da ke tsakanin ma'aurata, shawarwarin da suke bayarwa, shawarwarin da ba su bayar ba, da kuma yadda wani shiri zai iya canzawa a yanzu.
Turai ta fi kyau a matsayin tawagar har zuwa yanzu kuma tana kan gaba sosai kafin ranar karshe, amma wadannan wasannin biyu sun kuma nuna cewa Team USA tana da halin yaki wanda wasu, musamman Stateside, suka yi shakku a kai.
Turai ta ci 10-6 kafin ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup
Turai na kan gaba, kafin ranar karshe ta gasar cin kofin Ryder, bayan sun fita daga wasan da kwallaye hudu a ranar Asabar tare da 10-6 kan Amurka.
Ma'aurata masu ban sha'awa, Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari, sun ci nasara biyu a kan Tiger Woods mai gwagwarmaya kuma sun ɗaga ƙididdigar su a Le Golf National ta maki huɗu.
Kungiyar Turai ta Thomas Bjorn, da ke kokarin dawo da kwallo da suka rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ta yi nasara da wata tawagar Amurka da ta kasa farawa, a wasan kwallon hudu da aka yi da safe, inda ta ci 3-1.
Amurka ta fi yin adawa a wasannin biyu, inda suka ci wasanni biyu, amma ba su iya rage bambancin ba.
Kungiyar Jim Furyk za ta samu maki takwas a cikin wasanni 12 na mutum-mutumin ranar Lahadi, domin sake yin amfani da tubali.
Fleetwood shine farkon dan wasan Turai da ya ci maki hudu a jere, yayin da shi da Molinari, wanda aka sani da suna "Mollwood", bayan karshen mako mai ban mamaki, sune kawai biyu da suka ci maki hudu daga wasanni hudu na farko a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun doke Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan da kwallaye hudu a wasa, sai suka yi wasa sosai tare kuma suka ci Woods da dan wasan Amurka, Bryson Dechambeau a kan zobba tare da 5&4.
Woods, wanda ya yi tsalle a wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna a cikin babban wasa, amma yanzu ya rasa 19 daga cikin wasanni 29 tare da kwallaye hudu a wasa a kan wasanni biyu, kuma ya rasa bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda ya samu hutu a safiyar yau don wasannin da aka buga da kwallaye hudu, ya koma abokin wasansa, Henrik Stenson, a wasan biyu tare da 2&1 a kan Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka - lambobin daya da uku a duniya.
Koyaya, ƙungiyar Turai ba ta sami duk abin da take so ba a cikin kyakkyawan rana mai sanyi a cikin ra'ayi daga Paris.
Masu cin nasara sau uku na manyan gasa, Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas, sun daidaita matsayin Amurkawa da maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun sami nasara mai ban mamaki 2&1 a kan Mutanen Espanya Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter a wasan da kwallaye huɗu a wasa, kuma daga baya suka dawo kuma suka ci Poulter da Rory McIlroy 4&3 a wasan biyu, bayan sun rasa ramuka biyu na farko.
Sau biyu ne kawai a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup wata kungiya ta dawo bayan ta yi kasa da maki hudu kafin wasan daya, duk da cewa tawagar Furyk da ta yi nasara a bara, ta bukaci wasa daya kawai don sake dawo da matakin.
Bayan sun kasance a karo na biyu a rana, ba za su iya dawowa ranar Lahadi ba.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce a'a ta takaice  ga kawar da makamai a kai ba tare da amincewa ba
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa ci gaba da ikirarin ya kara rashin amincewa da Amurka kuma babu yiwuwar kasar ta daina makaman nukiliyarta a karkashin irin wannan yanayi.
Ri Yong Ho ya ce a taron majalisar dinkin duniya cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta yi "mahimman matakai na kyakkyawar niyya" a shekarar da ta gabata, daya daga cikinsu shi ne kawo karshen gwajin makaman nukiliya da makamai masu linzami, cire matsayin binciken nukiliya, da kuma bada alkawarin ta na girmamawa ba don kara yawan kayan aikin nukiliya ba.
"Amma ba mu ga irin wannan martani daga Amurka ba", in ji shi.
"Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba, ba za a iya amincewa da barazanar kasa ba, kuma a irin wannan yanayi ba lallai bane mu fara kwashe makamai da kanmu".
Yayin da Ri ya sake maimaita sanannen korafin da Washington ta yi na adawa da tsarin saurin kawar da makamai, wanda aka biya Koriya ta Arewa mataki-mataki, rahotonsa ya bayyana cewa ba su yi watsi da shirin kawar da makamai na Pyongyang ba.
Ri ya yi nuni da bayanin da Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump suka yi a taron kolin farko tsakanin shugaban Amurka da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga watan Yuni, lokacin da Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki kan "kashe makamai" a yankin Koriya ta Kudu, yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin tabbatar da tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi kokarin kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53, amma Amurka ta ce sai Pyongyang ta daina makaman nukiliyarta.
Washington ta kuma yi adawa da zargin da ake yi na daukar tsauraran matakai na kasa da kasa kan Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka ta dage kan shirin kare makamai da kuma kara amincewa da yarjejeniyar domin cimma burinta ta hanyar da ta dace, kuma tana adawa da kawo karshen yakin", in ji Ri.
"Abin da ya sa ya kamata mu yi imani da cewa 'yan Yammacin Turai za su iya saukar da mu shi ne burin mutanen da ba su san mu ba.
Amma matsalar ita ce, ci gaba da furci yana kara rashin amincewarmu.
Ri bai ambaci wani shiri na wani sabon taron kolin Kim da Trump ba, wanda shugaban Amurka ya haskaka a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon nan.
Ministan ya kuma yi nuni da ganawar da Kim ya yi da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu, Moon Jae-in sau uku a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata, ya kara da cewa: Idan matsalar kare makamai ta fito ne daga Koriya ta Kudu ba Amurka ba, to kare makaman yankin Koriya ba zai kasance a matsayin da yake a yanzu ba.
Wannan sanannen sautin muryar Ri ya sha bamban da na shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da ya ce a babban taron kasar, ba zai iya kaucewa cewa babban yankin Amurka ya zama manufa ta makamai masu linzami na Koriya ta Arewa ba, bayan da Shugaba Trump ya kira Kim dan makami mai linzami da shirin kashe kansa.
A Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a wannan shekarar, Trump, wanda a bara ya yi barazanar "kashe Koriya ta Arewa" ya yaba wa Kim saboda karfin gwiwar da ya nuna na daukar matakan kare makamansa, amma ya ce har yanzu akwai sauran aiki da yawa da za a yi, kuma dole ne a yi ikirarin cewa an riga an yi kafin Koriya ta Arewa ta kawar da makamanta.
A ranar Laraba ne Trump ya ce ba shi da wani lokaci, yana mai cewa "Ko shekara biyu, ko uku ko watanni biyar - komai".
Sin da Rasha sun ce ya kamata kwamitin tsaron na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya amince da Pyongyang kafin a dauki mataki.
Amma Sakataren harkokin wajen Amurka, Mike Pompeo, ya fadawa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar bikin cewa: "Tun da ake tilasta amincewa da amincewar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya dole ne a ci gaba da yin hakan da matuƙar aniya har sai mun ga cikakkiyar, karshe, tabbatar da kare makamai".
Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya kara yawan alkawuran da Koriya ta Arewa ta yi tun a shekarar 2006 a wani yunkuri na ragewa Pyongyang damar samun makaman nukiliya da makamai masu linzami.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a wajen taron na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya kuma ya ce bayan haka zai ziyarci Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya sabon taro.
Pompeo ya riga ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekarar, amma ziyarar ta karshe ba ta yi nasara ba.
Ya bar birnin Pyongyang a watan Yuli, inda ya ce an samu ci gaba, kafin Koriya ta Arewa ta tuhume shi da neman takardar karbar fansa.
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin, a wani taro da Moon a wannan watan, ta rushe wani tashar makami mai linzami da kuma wani tashar nukiliya idan Amurka ta yi wani "aiki na sararin samaniya".
Ya ce Kim ya gaya masa cewa, "har yanzu ana ci gaba da tattaunawa" da yake so, shi ne tabbatar da tsaro da Trump ya yi alkawari a Singapore da kuma matsawa zuwa ga dangantaka ta al'ada da Washington.
Dalibai a Harvard suna yin darasi don samun isasshen hutu
Wani sabon shiri a Jami'ar Harvard a wannan shekara ya ba masu karatu damar samun karin bacci, a kokarin da suke yi na yaki da karuwar yawan masu son yin karatu, na karantawa ta hanyar yin kofi a duk dare.
Wani masanin kimiyya ya yi gargadin cewa dalibai a manyan jami'o'i na duniya sau da yawa ba su da tabbaci sosai idan ya zo ga kula da kansu.
Charles Czeisler, malamin jami'a a fannin lafiyar bacci a Harvard Medical School kuma kwararre a asibitin Brigham and Women's, ya yi aikin da ya yi imanin shi ne na farko a Amurka.
Ya sami wahayi don yin wannan darasi bayan ya yi jawabi game da tasirin rashin bacci akan ilmantarwa.
"A ƙarshe, wani ya zo wurina ya ce, 'Me ya sa ba a sanar da ni wannan ba sai yanzu, a cikin shekaruna na ƙarshe?'
Ta ce babu wanda ya taba bayyana mata muhimmancin bacci - abin da ya ba ni mamaki", in ji shi a cikin wata hira da ya yi da jaridar The Telegraph.
Wannan bita, wanda aka fara gabatar da shi a wannan shekara, ya bayyana wa daliban manyan makarantu yadda halayen bacci ke taimakawa a fannin ilimi da kuma wasanni, tare da inganta jin daɗi da walwala.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar dan adam a Harvard Medical School kuma shugaban sashen kiwon lafiya na jami'ar, ya ce jami'ar ta zabi gabatar da wannan shirin ne bayan ta yi gargadin cewa dalibai suna fama da rashin bacci.
Hanyar da ke da tsawon sa'a daya tana da nau'o'in ayyukan haɗin kai.
A cikin wani ɓangare akwai hoto na ɗakin ajiya na yau da kullum, inda ɗalibai ke dogara da kofuna na kofi, labule, takalma da littattafai kuma an bayyana su game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske, da kuma yadda tasirin motsa jiki ya shafi rashin barci, da kuma muhimmancin barci.
A wani bangare kuma, ana ba dalibai rahoton yadda rashin bacci na dogon lokaci zai iya kara hadarin cututtukan zuciya, bugun jini, ciwon hauka da kuma ciwon daji.
Taswirar yankin jami'a, tare da gumakan ma'amala, sannan ya sa mahalarta suyi tunani game da aikin su na yau da kullun.
Mun san cewa ba zai canza halayyar dalibai ba.
Amma muna ganin suna da hakkin su san hakan - kamar yadda kuke da hakkin sanin illar da ke tattare da shan sigari," in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
"Mutumin da ke alfahari da kasancewa a duk dare" har yanzu yana nan, "in ji shi, "yana ƙara cewa fasahar zamani da kuma karuwar karuwar ɗalibai suna nuna cewa rashin bacci matsala ce mai girma.
Tabbatar da cewa kana da isasshen bacci, na bacci mai kyau, ya kamata ya zama makamin mai aminci na dalibi don yaƙi da ƙarfi, gajiya da damuwa, ya ce - har ma don kauce wa cin abinci, saboda rashin bacci yana sanya kwakwalwa cikin yanayin yunwa, yana sa su jin yunwa koyaushe.
Raymond So, dan California mai shekaru 19 da ke karatun ilimin lissafi da ilimin halittu, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Czeisler wajen tsara wannan darasi bayan ya dauki darasi daga wurinsa a shekararsa ta farko a Harvard.
Ya ce, fakin ya bude masa ido kuma ya sa ya nemi fakin a duk jami'ar.
Mataki na gaba, yana fatan, zai kasance don samun dalibi a ci gaba don kammala irin wannan hanya kafin su shiga cikin kamfanonin gasa.
Farfesa Czeisler ya shawarci dalibai da su sanya agogon sautin idan suna son su kwanta, da kuma lokacin da suke son su tashi, kuma su yi hattara da tasirin hasken shuɗi wanda hasken lantarki da hasken LED ke fitarwa, wanda zai iya sanya lokacin rana a cikin rashin tsari wanda zai sa ya zama da wahala a yi bacci.
