Almanac: Mai kirkirar Geigerteljar
Yanzu shafi daga Almanac dinmu na "Sunday Morning": 30 ga watan Satumba na 1882, shekaru 136 da suka wuce a yau da kuma ranar da aka haifi masanin kimiyyar halittu na gaba, Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a gidansa a Jamus.
Geiger ya ba da wata hanya ta kiyaye da kuma auna tasirin radiation, wani abu da ya haifar da abin da aka sani da geiger.
