Washington na iya auki rundunar soji idan ya cancanta domin hana makamashin Rasha cin kasuwa, har ma a yankin Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Ryan Zinke, wanda Washington Examiner ta nakalto.
Zinke ya yi ikirarin cewa ayyukan Rasha a Syria - musamman inda aka gayyace ta daga gwamnatin da ta amince da ita - na da matukar muhimmanci wajen gano sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Ina ganin dalilin da yasa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shine suna son sayar da makamashi, kamar yadda suke a Gabashin Turai, mafi kyawun sashi na Turai", in ji shi, bayan duk.
