Sabon jirgin ruwan sojin saman na Jamus ya kamata a fara aiki a shekarar 2014 a maimakon tsofaffin jiragen yakin Cold War, amma ba zai kasance ba har sai shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin tsari da kuma karuwar farashin, in ji kafofin watsa labarai na gida.
