A Palau, an kwashe mutane fiye da dubu goma sha shida bayan rashin nasarar.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Sulawest:
Palu babban birni ne na yankin tsakiyar Sulawesi, wanda ke kan wani kunkuntar rairayin bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, inda yawan jama'a a shekarar 2017 ya kai 379,800.
A shekara ta arba'in na bikin birnin, aka yi girgizar ƙasa kuma aka yi ambaliyar ruwa.
Donggala wata gwamnati ce da ke da nisan fiye da kilomita 300 (180 miles) na bakin teku a wani yanki na tsibirin Sulawesi.
A cikin gwamnati, wacce a zahiri ƙasa ɗaya ce, yawan jama'a ya kai 299,200 a 2017.
Kasuwancin kifi da noma sune manyan kayayyakin tattalin arzikin yankin na Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman a yankin bakin teku na Donggala.
Kayan kwalba ma yana da mahimmanci a cikin ƙasar, amma an tattara shi a Morowali, a kan rairayin bakin teku na Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fuskantar ambaliyar ruwa sosai a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938 wata guguwar tsunami ta kashe mutane sama da 200 kuma ta lalata gidaje da dama a Donggala.
Tsunami ya kuma afkawa West Dongola a shekarar 1996, inda mutane tara suka mutu.
Indonesia tana kan yankin girgizar kasa na Tekun Fasifik kuma tana fuskantar girgizar kasa akai-akai.
Ga wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar kasa da ambaliyar ruwa a zamanin nan:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin yankin Aceh na Arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya afkawa kasashe 14 kuma ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane sama da 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Wani jerin girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ya afkawa gabar yammacin Sumatra a karshen watan Maris da farkon watan Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane suka mutu a tsibirin Nias, a bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afka kudu da Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami da ya afkawa gabar tekun kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.6 ta afkawa kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin yankin Yammacin Sumatra.
Fiye da mutane 1100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5 ta afkawa daya daga cikin tsibiran Mentawai, nesa da Sumatra, inda ta haifar da ambaliyar ruwa mai karfin mita 10, wanda ya lalata garuruwa da dama da kuma kashe mutane kimanin 300.
2016: Girgizar kasa ta girgiza jihar Pidie Jaya ta Aceh, inda ta haifar da bala'i da kuma fargaba yayin da mutane ke tunawa da halakar da girgizar kasa da tsunami mai kisa ta 2004.
Babu wani ambaliyar ruwa da aka gani a wannan lokacin, amma fiye da mutane 100 sun mutu saboda gine-gine da suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia inda mutane sama da 500 suka mutu, mafi yawansu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar kasa ta lalata gine-gine dubbai kuma dubban masu yawon bude ido sun kasance a bakin teku na wucin gadi.
