Masu gabatar da kara a birnin New York na neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da laifin kai hari a birnin New York, inda mutane takwas suka mutu -- hukuncin kisa da ba a taba yi ba a jihar tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekaru 30, ya yi zargin cewa ya yi amfani da motar haya daga Home Depot don yin fashin a wani shagon sukari a West Side Highwat a Lower Manhattan, inda ya yi fashin mutane da masu sayar da sukari a kan hanyarsa a watan Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara dole ne su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya yi mummunan rauni, bisa ga takaddar da ke bin hukuncin kisa, da aka shigar a Kudancin New York.
A waɗannan laifuffuka biyu, shari'ar tana iya kai ga hukuncin kisa.
A mako bayan wannan taron, wani bincike na bincike ya ba Saipov tuhume-tuhume 22, ciki har da takwas na kisan kai ta hanyar ayyukan zalunci, wanda ake amfani da shi a cikin shari'ar Commonwealth a cikin shari'ar aikata laifuka, ciki har da zargin zalunci da lalata tare da wani abu.
