A baya bayan nan da aka soke hukuncin kisa a wani shari'ar tarayya a New York a 1953, ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan da aka yanke musu hukuncin kisa a cikin makircin yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
