Patrick Dwyer ya zira kwallaye biyu a Giants a Dundee
Dundee Stars sun biya diyya a wasan Elite League a ranar Juma'a ga Belfast Giants, inda suka ci wasan 5-3 a Dundee a ranar Asabar.
Giants sun sami saurin cin kwallaye biyu tare da bugun Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun sami gida a kan daidaitawa kafin Dwyer ya sake tura Giants a gaba.
Francois Bouchard ya daidaita Dundee, kafin kwallo biyu na Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya tabbatar musu da nasara.
Wannan ne karo na uku da kungiyar Elite League ta yi rashin nasara a kakar wasa ta bana ga dan wasan Adam Keefe, wanda ya dawo daga ci 2-1 da kuma cin Dundee a Belfast a ranar Juma'a.
Wannan shi ne karo na hudu da kungiyoyin suka hadu a wannan kakar, kuma Giants sun lashe wasanni uku.
Maganar farko ta Dwyer ta zo ne a minti na huɗu a 3:35 tare da wani bayani daga Kendall McFaull, kuma David Rutherford ya yi sharhi, lokacin da Beauvillier ya ninka jagorancin minti huɗu daga baya.
Abubuwa da yawa sun faru a farkon wasan kuma Sullivan ya dawo da gidan bayan 13:19, kafin Matt Marquardt ya zama mai gyara a raga na Cownie a 15:16.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da cewa Giants sun dauki jagorancin kafin mataki na farko, lokacin da ya zira kwallaye na karshe na maraice a ƙarshen farkon lokaci.
Ƙungiyar ta dawo kuma Bouchard ya sake daidaitawa da wata kalma lokacin da suke da mutum daya a kan gaba bayan 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun yi wasa tare, lokacin da Nielsen ya ba Dundee jagoranci a karon farko a wasan a ƙarshen lokacin, kuma ya tabbatar da nasara tare da cibiyar wasan ta biyar a tsakiyar lokacin.
